":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"真係咁"},{"pid":"f8b0b178c1bfd2d2a9b5e62b60917bba5efe35b1","tid":1891550,"uid":79085,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"我淨係知唔做一定冇用，感謝罷工醫護"},{"pid":"ad6a8a97e317dda212e81add48121cf1ad3bd7e8","tid":1891550,"uid":227139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:36:22.000Z","msg":"多謝醫護"},{"pid":"8598cc92a3632546dc2685ed027169365fc069b5","tid":1891550,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3097376bb5bed48aad3380ce704481c77b636555","tid":1891550,"uid":197561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:42:39.000Z","msg":"感謝醫護"},{"pid":"f0faf790d54051f6701211f0a024713d2dd7470f","tid":1891550,"uid":280648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終工會啱啱起步冇咩資金支持到罷工人員嘅生計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以都要啲時間先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9235aba41ae3af35da4dbe69e954cacee659336e","tid":1891550,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:45:52.000Z","msg":"救救醫護，工會做野，醫護集體大移民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fckKuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fckKuS</a>"},{"pid":"fd726c09c7f73c87fae57f4b33bfcd2d8c8e8d35","tid":1891550,"uid":128603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"感謝醫護。"},{"pid":"d6b7a8a7a20aea5f42aaa46b1293e433900b873e","tid":1891550,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T04