8515c116d2b722a41dcfb8630112","tid":1891550,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"五毛維穩account其中一個主要工作，無時無刻散播失敗論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db4192843bd897e415d6366e2e717e17af72dc4","tid":1891550,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"共狗 應對<br />\n分化工會 ，解<br />\n<br />\n感謝醫護帶頭"},{"pid":"39fe4718052d663a5b1c84aa033c9423cca52dd7","tid":1891550,"uid":166308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"專重醫護任何決定"}]}